---
title: Honey-Glazed Salmon & Roast Veggie Couscous with Mint Yoghurt
description: We’ve uncovered a real pearl for tonight’s dinner treat, a salmon coated in sweet honey on a cloud of
couscous. This bowl will be a real stunner with a dollop of mint yoghurt to freshen up. What a find!
